stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Collecting: ClickFullPage
  Collecting --> Capturing: CollectPageArtifacts ok
  Capturing --> Stitching: last frame placed
  Stitching --> Bundling: stitched png ready
  Bundling --> Downloading: zip ready
  Downloading --> Success: download started
  Idle --> PickerActive: ClickPick
  PickerActive --> Selecting: element picked
  Selecting --> Bundling: artifacts ready
  Success --> Idle: SUCCESS_AUTO_DISMISS_MS elapsed
  Collecting --> Error: any E_*
  Capturing --> Error: any E_*
  Stitching --> Error: any E_*
  Bundling --> Error: any E_*
  Downloading --> Error: E_DOWNLOAD_FAILED
  PickerActive --> Idle: Escape | Cancel
  Selecting --> Error: any E_*
  Error --> Collecting: Retry (was full page)
  Error --> PickerActive: Retry (was element)
  Error --> Idle: Escape
